name: Xpero Elhap Model
description:
This model is a custom blend of various models, presenting many options for generating images, including NSFW. Based on Stable Diffusion 1.5. Primarily focused on the creation of semi-realistic art. Can easily generate great images in different styles - realistic, art, etc.

The model is demanding for VAE, I use vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.

Caution. The model likes to give out NSFW content. Be careful what you ask for.
